<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-7">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-body">
        <h4>Lakes of Fire 2015 What Where When!</h4>
        <p>This guide is a volunteer project organized by the Info-Bot team. Submit your events below to be included in the printed WhatWhereWhen guide that will be handed out at the gate at Lakes of Fire! They will also be included in any mobile or web-apps about Lakes of Fire events. We reserve the right to make changes for clarity.</p>
        <p>Please use the <a href="/events.xml">XML feed</a> of this event guide for good! Contact Info-Bot at info-bot@lakesoffire.org with any questions or software bugs.</p>
        <p>Along with submitting an event, you can edit your event. Just remember to log in with the same account you used to create it. Events will no longer be editable once we send the guide to the printer.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-5">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-body">
        <h4>FABULOUS CONTRAPTION Event Requirements</h4>
        <p>Like <%= link_to "Lakes of Fire", "http://www.lakesoffire.org/blog/lof15-ticketing-procedures-gate-hours-gifting", target: "blank" %> itself, events in the What Where When guide must</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Start after Lakes of Fire starts at 12PM on June 17th</li>
          <li>End before Lakes of Fire ends at 3PM on June 21st</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Please note, all fields are required, but your contact information will only be used if we have questions about your submitted event.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> <!-- /row -->

<%= render partial: "event_form_header" %>

<div class="row">

  <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
    <div class="well"> 

      <% if @event %>
        <%= form_for @event, class: "form-inline" do |f| %>
          <h4>Add an Event</h4>

          <%= render 'event_form', f: f %>

          <%= submit_tag "Add", :class=>"btn btn-success" %>
        <% end %>
      <% else %>
        <p>Event submissions are closed.</p>
        <p>Download the <a href="/2015_LoF_WWW.pdf">2015 What Where When</a> guide!</p>
      <% end %>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <% current_day = nil %>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <a href="/events.xml" class="pull-right">XML</a>
        <h4>2015 Submitted Events</h4>

        <div class="row">
          <div class='col-md-12'>
            <a href="#yours" class="btn btn-default btn-xs pull-right btn-your-events">Yours</a>
            <a href="#all" class="btn btn-default btn-xs pull-right btn-all-events">All</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <% @events.each do |event| %>
          <% if current_day != event.current_event_time.starting.to_date %>
            <% current_day = event.current_event_time.starting.to_date %>
            <div class="row">
              <div class='col-md-12'>
                <h4><%= current_day.strftime("%A, %B #{current_day.day.ordinalize}") %></h4>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
          <div class="row <%= event.user == current_user ? "your-event" : "not-your-event" %>">
            <div class='col-md-12 <%= "event-#{event.id}" %>'>
              <%= link_to event do 
                    "#{event.title} - #{event.hosting_location} - #{event.current_event_time.starting.strftime("%l:%M %p")}"
                  end
              %>
              <% if event_is_editable?(event, current_user) %>
                <small><%= link_to "edit", edit_event_path(event), class: 'text-muted', style: "margin-left: 5px;" %></small>
              <% end %>
              <% if event.current_event_time.all_day %>
                <small class="text-info pull-right" style="margin-left: 5px;">all day!</small>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</div>
